{"backend_name": "GitHub", "backend_version": "0.25.1", "perceval_version": "0.13.0", "timestamp": 1585312407.343653, "origin": "https://github.com/hypertrons/hypertrons", "uuid": "559042cbe513c3805a53cec7752ed27931c3e764", "updated_on": 1580223452.0, "classified_fields_filtered": null, "category": "pull_request", "search_fields": {"item_id": "361711838", "owner": "hypertrons", "repo": "hypertrons"}, "tag": "https://github.com/hypertrons/hypertrons", "data": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hypertrons/hypertrons/pulls/221", "id": 361711838, "node_id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0MzYxNzExODM4", "html_url": "https://github.com/hypertrons/hypertrons/pull/221", "diff_url": "https://github.com/hypertrons/hypertrons/pull/221.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/hypertrons/hypertrons/pull/221.patch", "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hypertrons/hypertrons/issues/221", "number": 221, "state": "closed", "locked": false, "title": "feature: add md-lint(#210)", "user": {"login": "WuShaoling", "id": 16188599, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE2MTg4NTk5", "avatar_url": "https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/16188599?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling", "html_url": "https://github.com/WuShaoling", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "body": "Feature: add md-lint mentioned in #210 \r\n\r\n### Feature\r\n\r\nImplement markdown file format checking based on [remark](https://www.npmjs.com/package/remark).\r\n\r\nThe rules are declared in the file `app/utils/md-lint/index.ts`.\r\n\r\nReferenced from: \r\n- [remark-preset-lint-markdown-style-guide](https://www.npmjs.com/package/remark-preset-lint-markdown-style-guide)\r\n- [remark-preset-lint-recommended](https://www.npmjs.com/package/remark-preset-lint-recommended)\r\n\r\nParameters have been partially modified, and `remark-lint-maximum-line-length` has been cancelled.\r\n\r\n### Configuration\r\nThe configuration is defined as follows\uff1a\r\n```\r\ninterface Config {\r\n  patterns: string[];\r\n  options: {\r\n    useGitIgnore?: boolean;\r\n    usePackageJson?: boolean;\r\n    configKey?: string;\r\n    gitIgnoreFile?: string;\r\n    ignore?: string[];\r\n    cwd?: string;\r\n  };\r\n}\r\n```\r\n- `patterns` declares which files need to be checked. The default is `['** / *. md']`\r\n- The definition of `options` is the same as the definition in deglob, the default is\r\n   ```\r\n   {\r\n      useGitIgnore: true,\r\n      ignore: [ 'node_modules/**/*' ],\r\n   }\r\n   ```\r\n\r\nConfiguration can be configured in the package.json file.\r\n```\r\n{ \r\n   \"md-lint\": {\r\n      \"patterns\": [\r\n        \"**/*.md\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"options\": {\r\n        \"useGitIgnore\": true,\r\n        \"ignore\": [\r\n          \"node_modules/**/*\"\r\n        ]\r\n      }\r\n   }\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Run\r\n- run locally: `npm run md-lint`\r\n- run in CI: `npm run lint`\r\n\r\n### Notes:\r\nYou can use `-`,` * `or` + `for unordered lists in markdown. `remark-lint-unordered-list-marker-style` restricts the the unordered list format, the parameters include: `consistent`, `-`, `*`. We use the default parameter `consistent` (`consistent` detects the first used list style and warns when subsequent lists use different styles.)\r\n\r\nSigned-off-by: WuShaoling <wsl6@outlook.com>", "created_at": "2020-01-11T09:11:53Z", "updated_at": "2020-01-28T14:57:32Z", "closed_at": "2020-01-12T12:13:06Z", "merged_at": "2020-01-12T12:13:06Z", "merge_commit_sha": "0e43cb0e10d4e23c16c110acb212c147ad3d65dc", "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [{"id": 1701589789, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxNzAxNTg5Nzg5", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hypertrons/hypertrons/labels/kind/feature", "name": "kind/feature", "color": "c7def8", "default": false, "description": "Category issues or prs related to feature request."}, {"id": 1725641498, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxNzI1NjQxNDk4", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hypertrons/hypertrons/labels/pull/approved", "name": "pull/approved", "color": "008672", "default": false, "description": "If a pull is approved, it will be automatically merged"}], "milestone": null, "draft": false, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hypertrons/hypertrons/pulls/221/commits", "review_comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hypertrons/hypertrons/pulls/221/comments", "review_comment_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hypertrons/hypertrons/pulls/comments{/number}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hypertrons/hypertrons/issues/221/comments", "statuses_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/hypertrons/hypertrons/statuses/2e31cbf76b9a08012e434bdae2ae28c79f26ad9c", "head": {"label": "WuShaoling:md-lint", "ref": "md-lint", "sha": "2e31cbf76b9a08012e434bdae2ae28c79f26ad9c", "user": {"login": "WuShaoling", "id": 16188599, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjE2MTg4NTk5", "avatar_url": "https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/16188599?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling", "html_url": "https://github.com/WuShaoling", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/WuShaoling/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.